{
  "chapter": 9,
  "chapter_summary": "第九回　销魂秘笈。剑客行故事继续。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "雷大叔",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "雷大叔",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他怎地完全知道我的心事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "雷大叔",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我怎地竟连这道理都想不出来，",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "雷大叔",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "瞎子摸象",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "雷大叔",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "雷大叔",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "忍不住抢口道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "雷大叔",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "雷大叔",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道这本书在有光的地方就看不见了吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "叭",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "雷大叔",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "雷大叔",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "雷大叔",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他语声一顿，突又将这本怪绝天下，也妙绝天下的奇书，送到展白面前，又道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "雷大叔",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "美人有态有情有趣有神，唇檀拂日，媚体迎风……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "雷大叔",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "雷大叔",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "晚辈这些日子以来，日日都在摸索，已将此书上的字迹完全默诵出来——",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "雷大叔",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "雷大叔",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他缓缓张开眼睛，退回石床坐下，又道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他语声渐渐地变得高昂起来：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "雷大叔",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哼",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "雷大叔",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "雷大叔",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "雷大叔",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他微笑稍歇，又道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哼",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他此刻心中对这",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "雷大叔",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "雷大叔",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "雷大叔",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "雷大叔",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因之他才费尽心力，制了如此一本奇书，藏在罗浮绝顶的一个隐秘所在，而且扬言天下，有如此一部奇书，只是直言定力不坚的，切切不可尝试——",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "雷大叔",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你方才见这书中之人，是否神态各异，但面目却完全一样，唉——这魔女当真是天生尤物，便只这画里传真，已能使人意马心猿，也难怪那'只眼郎君'——",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只眼郎君",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "雷大叔",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他指了指",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "雷大叔",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是极！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "雷大叔",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "雷大叔",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "雷大叔",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "展白颔首一叹，却听",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "雷大叔",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "雷大叔",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此种情况，这两人想必都难逃毒手了吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "雷大叔",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    }
  ],
